        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Hospice Safe Drug Disposal Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Controlled Substances Act to allow a hospice employee to handle the lawfully dispensed controlled substances of a deceased hospice patient to assist with disposal of the controlled substances.</p>]]></text>
